    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of producing designs or pictures (as on wood or leather) by burning or scorching with hot instruments.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
